== 短篇動畫 ==
2019年3月11日，[[Production_I.G|Production I.G]]宣佈旗下分公司[[WIT_STUDIO|WIT STUDIO]]將會把《外之國的少女》改編成10分鐘的短篇[[原創動畫錄影帶|原創動畫錄影帶]]，由久保雄太郎和米谷聰美執導，並會在同年9月10日與日文版的第8卷單行本一起捆綁發售<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.production-ig.co.jp/hotnews/2019/031101.html |title=「とつくにの少女」のアニメ化が決定！ |website=[[Production_I.G|Production I.G]] |date=2019-03-11 |accessdate=2020-09-11 |language=ja |archive-date=2019-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331174020/https://www.production-ig.co.jp/hotnews/2019/031101.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。WIT STUDIO稱他們在創作過程中實驗性地使用了新的表達手法<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-03-08/the-girl-from-the-other-side-siuil-a-run-manga-gets-original-anime-dvd/.144340 |last=Sherman |first1=Jennifer |title=''The Girl From the Other Side: Siúil, a Rún'' Manga Gets Original Anime DVD |website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=2019-03-08 |accessdate=2019-03-08 |archive-date=2019-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190324104825/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-03-08/the-girl-from-the-other-side-siuil-a-run-manga-gets-original-anime-dvd/.144340 |dead-url=no|language=en }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Hodgkins |first1=Crystalyn |title=Wit Studio Previews ''The Girl from the Other Side'' Anime Short in Video |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-09-07/wit-studio-previews-the-girl-from-the-other-side-anime-short-in-video/.150847 |website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |accessdate=2020-04-28 |date=2019-09-07 |archive-date=2019-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203163002/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-09-07/wit-studio-previews-the-girl-from-the-other-side-anime-short-in-video/.150847 |dead-url=no |language=en}}</ref>。在單行本發行前，OVA曾在2019年8月1日於[[蒙特利爾|蒙特利爾]]{{link-en|加拿大奇幻電影節|Fantasia International Film Festival}}短暫首映<ref>{{cite web |last1=Hodgkins |first1=Crystalyn |title=Montreal's Fantasia Festival Screens World Premiere of ''The Girl from the Other Side'', ''Shishigari''